name: Quack Capital
description: The Busiest Duck on the Block(chain) Quack Capital is a hybrid utility project that aims to combine the best between SPL and NFT communities on Solana, they aim to be continuously shipping products to ultimately drive value back to $QUACK SPL and NFT holders all organically. - Cool retro design - Quack map - Staking - Hybrid portal - Quack message - Gameified staking - NFT game and claw machine On top of the stack of tech products built by Quack, they also plan to include referrals and develop themselves as a strong community in the Solana ecosystem. Whatever the community wants to build, Quack has the resources.
